comment: Mudiay (DEN) does not establish a legal guarding position as he slides to his right initiating the contact with Wall (WAS).
Beal (WAS) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Mudiay's (DEN) drive. Any contact on the play is initiated by Mudiay.
[Incidental or immaterial] Harris (DEN) grabs and holds Nene's (WAS) jersey, affecting his FOM.
Faried (DEN) obtains a legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Temple (WAS) that does not affect his RSBQ.
Correctly called OOB last touched by Harris (DEN). Washington retained possession.
Faried (DEN) obtains a legal guarding position and cleanly blocks Beal's (WAS) dunk attempt.
Beal (WAS) legally contests Barton's (DEN) jump shot attempt.

After communicating with the Replay Center, there was conclusive video evidence that showed that Wall (WAS) did not touch the ball prior to it going OOB. The ruling on the court was overturned and Washington was awarded possession.
Nene (WAS) sets the screen on Barton (DEN) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Beal (WAS) makes contact with Gallinari (DEN) that affects his RSBQ.
Beal (WAS) commits a take foul on Mudiay (DEN).
Dudley (WAS) commits a take foul during rebounding on Faried (DEN).
Harris (DEN) makes contact with Wall's (WAS) arm and body that affects his driving layup attempt.
Nene (WAS) sets the screen on Mudiay (DEN) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Beal (WAS) and Mudiay (DEN) make incidental foot to foot contact away from the ball that causes Mudiay to fall to the floor.
Beal (WAS) grabs the ball prior to any incidental contact with Mudiay's (DEN) arm.
Dudley (WAS) clamps Faried's (DEN) arm, affecting his ability to retrieve the rebound.
Barton (DEN) grabs Beal (WAS) affecting his FOM away from the ball.
Mudiay (DEN) sets the screen on Nene (WAS) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Nene (WAS) commits a take foul on Gallinari (DEN).
[Incidental or immaterial] Dudley (WAS) purposely makes contact with the ball after the made basket, which prevents the opposing team from quickly inbounding the ball.
Temple (WAS) commits a take foul on Barton (DEN).
